    "Chandra Asri Petrochemical teamed with French tire manufacturer Michelin in 2015 to develop a synthetic rubber plant in Indonesia.",
    "In March 2022, the Pangestu family bought a third of Star Energy - which has controlling stakes in leading  Indonesian geo-thermal projects-  from Thailand?s BCPG Public Company for $440 million."
